      Standstill
   =20
 =20
A small lawyer point. Here is the standstill agreement that Elon Musk signe=
d with Twitter on Monday. It has three numbered paragraphs: (1) Musk will j=
oin the board, (2) he won=E2=80=99t go above 14.9% of the stock as long as =
he=E2=80=99s on the board (and for 90 days after he leaves), and (3) a tiny=
 bit of legal boilerplate. It=E2=80=99s great! This is the sort of thing th=
at lawyers can do if they put their minds to it. If the richest person in t=
he world is like =E2=80=9CI want to be on the board, in exchange I will agr=
ee to a standstill, and I don=E2=80=99t want any other nonsense,=E2=80=9D t=
hen he will get this agreement. And you can read it in like one minute and =
