</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There is one main reason to do a fake =
takeover of a public company. You buy some stock in the company. You announ=
ce a fake takeover: Put out a fake press release saying the company has agr=
eed to a merger, or put out a press release (or SEC filing) saying that you=
 are doing a tender offer for the company at a premium. People read the fak=
e announcement and think it=E2=80=99s real, so the stock price goes up. You=
 sell your stock before they notice it=E2=80=99s fake. You slink away and h=
ope you don=E2=80=99t get caught. (If you get caught you <a href=3D"https:/=
/link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/27277787.256598/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxv=
b21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTUtMDYtMDQvZ3V5LXdoby1kaWQtYXZvbi1=
ob2F4LXdhcy10ZXJyaWJsZS1hdC1ob2F4ZXM_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDQwNjIyX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdX=
RtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjIwNDA2JnV0b=
V9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBfbc01211" itemprop=3D"=
StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #00000=
0; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-botto=
m-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> get=
 in trouble</a>.)</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That is the main reason t=
o do a fake takeover. There are=C2=A0others! Elon Musk <a href=3D"https://l=
ink.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/27277787.256598/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb2=
1iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTgtMDgtMDgvZWxvbi1tdXNrLWhhcy1zb21lL=
WZ1bi13aXRoLXRlc2xhP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA0MDYyMl9NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1h=
