background-color: #ccc;"> did one</a>=C2=A0on=C2=A0Tesla Inc. for no discer=
nible=C2=A0reason; he was bored on Twitter, I guess, and kind of annoyed th=
at Tesla=E2=80=99s stock price was too low. He <a href=3D"https://link.mail=
.bloombergbusiness.com/click/27277787.256598/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLm=
NvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTgtMDktMjgvbXVzay1zLXRlc2xhLWZ1bi1kb2VzLW5vd=
C1hbXVzZS1zZWM_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDQwNjIyX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1=
